# Instructions

Return a SINGLE JSON object conforming exactly to this schema. Do not
emit prose outside the JSON.

```json
{{
  "cluster_id": {cluster_id},
  "cell_type": "<one of the candidates above, or 'Unknown' if none fits>",
  "confidence": <float in [0, 1]>,
  "evidence_markers": [
    {{"gene": "<gene name from the candidate's supporting_markers above>", "de_rank": <int>, "db_source": "<source>", "db_celltype": "<the same cell_type>", "weight": <float>}}
