# Hard constraints (your output will be rejected if any are violated)

1. `cell_type` MUST be one of the candidates above, or "Unknown".
2. `evidence_markers` MUST be non-empty unless `cell_type == "Unknown"`.
3. Every entry in `evidence_markers` MUST come from the supporting_markers
   list of the chosen candidate above — do not invent markers.
4. `narrative` MUST quote at least one specific value (gene name, NMI value,
   purity value, or cluster id) from the cluster context above.
